hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDonald Trump 唔係唔得，但大家都知Americans唔係咁鐘意佢indeed<br />\n<br />\n小朋友版本，應該易學啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要好似學唱榮光咁 學熟背熟 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP38q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=89b567ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G7yPHhB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG7yPHhB.jpg&h=cbf3c5a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />HKAA 個tg合唱團grp: @USAanthemchoirhk<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歌詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/20/000540_03276b5929c6dce47983814ecebc56d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F20%2F000540_03276b5929c6dce47983814ecebc56d8.jpg&h=6ad07795&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />9.20 大合唱<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9uNMKxA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9uNMKxA.jpg&h=fb7daf54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGo this one tmr first!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>日後要再舉辦多啲呢類活動呀</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLast not least<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">驅逐共黨 光復香港<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"ea3d89899518a2744baf0ea0dae33a9ae2fda344","tid":1581681,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:19:25.000Z","msg":"【行動post/多圖】922和你suck 8大行動（更新版）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581619</a><br />\n<br />\n【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span 